> +./notworking.zsh:4> path=3D'exiftime not found'
> +./notworking.zsh:5> [[ 1 -ne 0 ]]
> +./notworking.zsh:6> prog=3Didentify
> +./notworking.zsh:7> path=3D+./notworking.zsh:7> which identify
> +./notworking.zsh:7> path=3D'identify not found'
> %
>=20
> Any idea?

